metadata.title: NATIONAL WETLANDS INVENTORY - ALASKA
metadata.description: Data Type: Vegetation/Land Cover/Soils;   Wetlands maps with classification according to USFWS' "Classification of Wetlands and Deepwater Habitats of the United states." Wetlands information is interpreted from high-altitude, color infrared photography, primarily at the scale of 1:60,000. Maps are produced at scales of 1:63,360 or 1:40,000.
